The paper discusses improving memory hierarchy utilization for stencil computations on multicore machines, which involves parallel computing and memory optimization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.PF (Performance), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.AR (Architecture), cs.MS (Mathematical Software), and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
